{"tid":1335814,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日不如返歸睇動畫算","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T06:16:34.000Z","uid":198822,"like":75,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f1dd77e3821690261eaf6099767123276a604879","tid":1335814,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係更加肯定嘅係，聽日唔出，<span style=\"color: gold;\">往後幾十年都會質疑自己2019年7月21日做咗啲咩。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢家已經死咗4個手足：<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9MYvnmXUAAWcLT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9MYvnmXUAAWcLT.jpg&h=5d757b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dqs1Rei.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqs1Rei.png&h=c9d58ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2385000/2388598/65291886_2294255220824150_714826323494699008_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2385000%2F2388598%2F65291886_2294255220824150_714826323494699008_n_1024.jpg&h=7ed0bfdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw/photos/2019/07/05/1562294650-5d1eb97a4e6d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fphotos%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F1562294650-5d1eb97a4e6d1.jpg&h=6400fde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟衷心希望各位動漫台手足諗多次，點解佢地要選擇以死明志。<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為佢地唔想我地忘記；因為佢地想用以死明志嘅手段，換嚟香港嘅勝利 。</span><br />\n<br />\n捫心自問，七月開始，有冇幾絲倦怠，有冇開始捉唔緊六月飛霜、義士殞落個時，悲憤嘅感觸？<br />\n<br />\n小弟都有，亦都好驚。我相信四位手足一直望住我地。佢地好想知道，自己放棄咗生存落去嘅權利，為香港換嚟啲咩。係一石激起千重浪？定係石入死水，波瀾不驚？我好驚自己會唔記得咗呢個時空之下，區區一片殖民地竟然培育過咁多善良、勇敢、曾經抱有希望、又將希望放入我地手心嘅志士。<br />\n<br />\n香港要革命，其實好難。反送中運動行到今日，其實有好大機會走上當初雨革嘅舊路，慢慢失卻民心，弭息於無形。但係如果早料到會咁，點解四位手足要選擇咁做，用遲早會被淡忘嘅方式離開人世？<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地始終相信香港人。相信縱身一跳會濺起一啲水花，滋潤一撮泥土，幫到幾粒種子萌芽。如果四位手足唔愛香港愛到咁，就唔會有七一嘅死士，就唔會有每次地區遊行留守到最後嘅新一代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/1200x800/public/d8/images/methode/2019/07/07/28f99690-9fbd-11e9-baa5-dd214ed0de8f_image_hires_111426.JPG?itok=RaGLyUR3&amp;v=1562469276\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F1200x800%2Fpublic%2Fd8%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2F28f99690-9fbd-11e9-baa5-dd214ed0de8f_image_hires_111426.JPG%3Fitok%3DRaGLyUR3%26v%3D1562469276&h=acf6b86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/july-1-legco-storming-china-extradition-9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fjuly-1-legco-storming-china-extradition-9.jpeg&h=a806ee2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cc6e123b-032a-48dd-af09-e916e67cb9d0-1_avvPV_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcc6e123b-032a-48dd-af09-e916e67cb9d0-1_avvPV_1200x0.png&h=c7fcf511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅犧牲，只能夠由我地嚟賦予意義。以往呢幾個星期之中，已經有無數香港人行出嚟用行動、用血汗，話畀四位手足，講畀香港知，為咗一場政治風波獻身嘅意義在於邊度。<br />\n<br />\n每個人嘅底線唔同，但係聽日721最低限度，企出嚟，用腳步為石屎馬路印上血肉嘅溫度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUdnRb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUdnRb7.png&h=6bab3358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30447dcc12f0d70ca818c2edcf8dad4998603750","tid":1335814,"uid":149878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"4d19da9a7ee9535dd432c8bb659392cf1f82e2b4","tid":1335814,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"新盾牌教學2&mdash;空樽護甲（快入！！！！）長期置頂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334262</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2ee28052e07d5b3e3d6d5765266b9bcf08b3092","tid":1335814,"uid":39181,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係諗住聽日係屋企睇動畫"},{"pid":"395ec4bf820fafbd653da7d573764cb01fd625f0","tid":1335814,"uid":242323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"721 push"},{"pid":"217d8f8f040da01a9d9c98688cefecf648c91e1c","tid":1335814,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2ee28052e07d5b3e3d6d5765266b9bcf08b3092","tid":1335814,"uid":39181,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係諗住聽日係屋企睇動畫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"朝早睇，晏晝出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c39710fa630a4cc219b9b2b7077f68d5b854e15","tid":1335814,"uid":476,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"已安在家中 有心<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"e54ac69513c49124f3da722092ca2fa5bbd0e48f","tid":1335814,"uid":110507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"幫手po個ig fb 叫多d人出黎 加油!<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/21/003736_ed4a7014ec0ddb523eed5eca3f8b85f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F21%2F003736_ed4a7014ec0ddb523eed5eca3f8b85f9.jpg&h=6bb5359c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/21/003743_7e9fb5668e34e02b455ee3bdbb815d0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F21%2F003743_7e9fb5668e34e02b455ee3bdbb815d0e.png&h=2eb4229c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/21/003750_07deeadead6c0fadd2c8b2ea2a380a2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F0